:: Public Holidays
"Fête du Nouvel An"                           public cultural on 1.1
"Fête annuelle des religions traditionnelles" public religious on 10.1
"Lundi de Pâques"                             public religious on easter plus 1 days
"Fête du travail"                             public cultural on 1.5.
"Jour de l’Ascension"                         public religious on easter plus 39 days
"Lundi de Pentecôte"                          public religious on easter plus 50 days
"Fête nationale"                              public cultural on 1.8.
"Jour de l’Assomption"                        public religious on 15.8.
"Jour de la Toussaint"                        public religious on 1.11.
"Jour de Noël"                                public religious on 25.12.
"Jour de Maouloud"                            public religious on hijri rabialawal 12
"Jour du Ramadan"                             public religious on hijri shawwal 1
"Jour de la Tabaski"                          public religious on hijri thualhijjah 10

